comments:
During the deletion of the first row, the selection changes from 2 rows to 1
row. The selection change event is sent out, which invoke 
GraphicalEditorWithFlyoutPalette.convertEventToGFE. This method do a special
case for the selection with 1 row,

if ( size == 1 && list.get( 0 ) instanceof RowHandle )
{
....
}

while in this time, the dirty variable on GridEditPart is false. So, the method
retrieves an obsolete grid row information, which causes a NPE.
